nodes.bodyText: Isn't this going to copy the entire map?

I had to add SearchError to the Swagger for the sake of JS/TS, but it's my understanding that this is a subset of a well-defined error contract for Microsoft REST APIs. Do we actually need to expose this, or is there some Azure Core type for error payloads that overlaps SearchError?
